        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">Boolean</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>Boolean that if it is set to true and there are multiple images returned the most recent will be returned. If it is set to false and there are multiple images return the datasource will error.</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="name_yaml">

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>Name of the image being searched for. Cannot be used with name_regex or arn.</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="nameregex_yaml">

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>Regular expression name of the image being searched for. Cannot be used with arn or name.</dd><dt class="property-optional"

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>The type of image which must be (PUBLIC, PRIVATE, or SHARED).</dd></dl>
